Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.45,0:17:45.46,Cart_C_Tre,CARTEL,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HD0B0AF&\c&H383533&\an1\bord5\fs12\blur0.4\pos(308,314)}Touko Usagihara
